  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The biggest entry in the series yet!Each minigame lasts around 2–3 minutes, packed with a wide variety of fast-paced competitive and cooperative challenges.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports local multiplayer and co-op, as well as Remote Play Together.<br>Jump in and enjoy instant fun with family and friends!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Free Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/ffabef4566b7892f9032678f7942d61e.poster.avif?t=1773042033\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/ffabef4566b7892f9032678f7942d61e.webm?t=1773042033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/ffabef4566b7892f9032678f7942d61e.mp4?t=1773042033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick a game freely and play!With both competitive and cooperative games, there are lots of ways to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In single-player mode, record your high scores and compete against players from around the world!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Party Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a selection of games to play in order, and compete to become the champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can select the option to double the points in the last game!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Character Edit]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/c2d1b509fd4083a646f73c7a9943ade8.poster.avif?t=1773042033\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/c2d1b509fd4083a646f73c7a9943ade8.webm?t=1773042033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/c2d1b509fd4083a646f73c7a9943ade8.mp4?t=1773042033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your ideal hero and bring your unique flair to the party!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To receive news and update notifications</strong><br>Please click on <strong>Developer: SAT-BOX</strong> at the top of the store page and <strong>Follow</strong> us!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The biggest entry in the series yet!Each minigame lasts around 2–3 minutes, packed with a wide variety of fast-paced competitive and cooperative challenges.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports local multiplayer and co-op, as well as Remote Play Together.<br>Jump in and enjoy instant fun with family and friends!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Free Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/ffabef4566b7892f9032678f7942d61e.poster.avif?t=1773042033\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/ffabef4566b7892f9032678f7942d61e.webm?t=1773042033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/ffabef4566b7892f9032678f7942d61e.mp4?t=1773042033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick a game freely and play!With both competitive and cooperative games, there are lots of ways to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In single-player mode, record your high scores and compete against players from around the world!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Party Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a selection of games to play in order, and compete to become the champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can select the option to double the points in the last game!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Character Edit]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315600/extras/c2d1b509fd4083a646f73c7a9943ade8.poster.avif?t=1773042033\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea